text: CALD may refer to: * Cambridge Advanced Learner's Dictionary * Council of Asian Liberals and Democrats * Council of Australian Law Deans * Culturally and linguistically diverse, a term used in policy discourse related to multiculturalism in Australia * former NASDAQ symbol between 2000 and 2001 of Caldera Systems, Inc. * former NASDAQ symbol between 2001 and 2001 of Caldera International, Inc. * NASDAQ symbol since 2003 of CallidusCloud ==See also== * Caldesmon, protein encoded by the CALD1 gene
title: CALD
